---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Rules & Regulations | Romillie Hadeljo">
  <div class="bg-emerald-950 min-h-screen text-stone-200">
    <main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">Rules & Regulations</h1>
        
        <p class="text-emerald-200/60 mb-12 text-lg italic">To ensure a comfortable and safe stay for all our guests, we kindly ask you to adhere to the following house rules.</p>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Documentation -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6">1. Identification</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">In accordance with local regulations, all guests (including children) must provide a valid government-issued photo ID upon check-in. Foreign nationals must provide a valid Passport and Visa.</p>
          </section>

          <!-- Conduct -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6">2. Guest Conduct</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-300 space-y-4">
              <li class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Quiet Hours:</strong> Please maintain silence in corridors and common areas between 10:00 PM and 7:00 AM.</li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Visitors:</strong> For security reasons, outside visitors are not permitted in guest rooms. You may meet your visitors in the common lounge area until 9:00 PM.</li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Dress Code:</strong> Guests are requested to be appropriately dressed when in common areas of the guesthouse.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Safety & Prohibitions -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6">3. Prohibited Activities</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-300 space-y-4">
              <li class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Smoking:</strong> Romillie Hadeljo is a strictly non-smoking property. A cleaning fee will be charged for smoking in rooms.</li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Illegal Substances:</strong> Possession or consumption of illegal drugs is strictly prohibited and will be reported to the authorities immediately.</li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed"><strong>Hazardous Items:</strong> Storage of explosive, flammable, or hazardous materials inside the rooms is not allowed.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Property Care -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6">4. Property & Damages</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Guests are responsible for any damage caused to the property, furniture, or equipment. The cost of repair or replacement will be charged to the guest's account.</p>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">Please ensure all electrical appliances (lights, geysers, heaters) are turned off when leaving your room to conserve energy.</p>
          </section>

          <!-- Food & Drink -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6">5. Food & Dining</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">To maintain hygiene and prevent pests, we request guests to avoid consuming heavy or odorous food inside the guest rooms. Please use the designated dining area for all meals.</p>
          </section>

          <!-- Management Rights -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6">6. Management's Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">The management reserves the right to ask any guest to vacate the premises in case of violation of house rules or behavior that disturbs the peace of other guests, without any refund.</p>
          </section>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center text-emerald-200/40 text-sm italic">
          <p>Thank you for your cooperation and for choosing Romillie Hadeljo.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
